    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "937023_7_2730-2745",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2730-2745",
      "markText": "瘸子送的那半个橙子被我弄丢了。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=937023&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2730&rangeEnd=2745",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e8323d05e4c3f5e8117492?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2730&rangeEnd=2745"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "937023_6_3840-3906",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3840-3906",
      "markText": "那时候我还不知道，这一生都不会再见到爱德华多了，也无从得知他的命运如何，只剩下记忆中那双在一顶可笑的水手帽下被泪水漫过的黑色大眼睛。",
      "totalCount": 266,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=937023&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3840&rangeEnd=3906",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e8323d05e4c3f5e8117492?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3840&rangeEnd=3906"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "937023_15_3191-3249",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "3191-3249",
      "markText": "等修女们走了，我就问艾莱娜，是谁告诉修女长我们俩是玛利亚太太和上帝先生的孩子的。艾莱娜没有回答，只是抽了我一个嘴巴。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=937023&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3191&rangeEnd=3249",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e8323d05e4c3f5e8117492?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3191&rangeEnd=3249"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "937023_16_1902-1939",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1902-1939",
      "markText": "我们从来没见过那么胖的人，你回想一下你见过的最胖的人，然后把那人放大四倍。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=937023&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1902&rangeEnd=1939",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5e8323d05e4c3f5e8117492?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1902&rangeEnd=1939"
    },
    {
